lead_paragraph: Jon Lester sought out Kyle Hendricks in the clubhouse, telling him the only thing that would have made his night better was if he had hit a solo homer for the game's only run.

headline.print_headline: Hendricks Pitches 7-Hitter as Cubs Beat Marlins 5-0
